      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_49456456809734425.png",
                "id": "talent83787",
                "key": "行幡鳴弦",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "行幡鳴弦"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">優風傾姿</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">優風傾姿</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行「普通攻擊」時：</span>造成的傷害+2；如果敵方存在後臺角色，則此技能改為對下一個敵方後臺角色造成傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/052cd901b44cef8359f0bebb98404194_3633376289215157159.png",
                "id": "talent13314",
                "key": "羽畫‧風姿華歌",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "羽畫‧風姿華歌"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成7點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>；如果角色附屬有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">優風傾姿</span>，則將其移除並使此傷害+1。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">優風傾姿</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行「普通攻擊」時：</span>造成的傷害+2；如果敵方存在後臺角色，則此技能改為對下一個敵方後臺角色造成傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/5a55e705974f27b8bb86c628019d5ad9_437844653247232064.png",
                "id": "talent38318",
                "key": "狂言‧式樂五番",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "狂言‧式樂五番"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_3012314943012861018.png",
